Author: meowmehungry
Text: Omg this happens to me too!

Author: Althbird
Text: I feel this - I’m not by any means tiny like I used to be; but when Ive told people my weight they’re like “where is it though?” It’s very obvious I see me differently than everyone else. Not just because of what other people say, but because sometimes I’ll walk by a mirror or a window and it’s like a catch a glimpse of what I really look like and I have to do a double take because the girl I occasionally see isn’t disgusting, or ‘bad’ looking. Unfortunately, when I do the double cake she’s never there, but hopefully one day I’ll catch her
